#: ../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:520
#: a05264491cb44655b69f10858842c7f8
msgid "可以，通过二次开发的方式进行实现"
msgstr "Yes. It can be implemented through secondary development."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:523
#: dddf3f847c914b82af9be80505bb93a0
msgid "请问UWB基站应用部署一般需要几个呢？"
msgstr ""
"How many base stations are generally needed for UWB base station deployment?"

